&lt;br/&gt;
ant  -Dmvnrepo=&lt;a href=&quot;http://myrepo.org/maven&quot;&gt;http://myrepo.org/maven&lt;/a&gt; -Dhadoop-core.version=0.20.myversion -Dhadoop-test.version=0.20.myversion</customfieldvalue>

